      "name": "Non-cannulated pedicle screw applicability domain",
      "description": "Model predictions are applicable only to non-cannulated Ti-6Al-4V pedicle screws with outer diameter 7.0–8.0 mm and thread pitch 2.75–3.25 mm, tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending at room temperature (18–25 °C) using polyacetal blocks with density 0.08–0.12 g/cm³. Extrapolation to cannulated designs, diameters outside this range, or dynamic fatigue loading is explicitly excluded."
    },
